				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Current work on distinguishing different dark energy models without tedious numerical calculations.<br />
<span id="more-2327"></span><br />
2011-12-16:<br />
Tower Wang is here to help.<br />
2011-12-17:<br />
Changed from hubble distance to particle horizon; Changed the equation for growth factor, considering the dynamic dark energy.<br />
2011-12-18:<br />
Still have a problem in matter power spectrum. Working on the mathematica notebook file today, hoping to find out what is wrong.<br />
I found some mistakes in Ivan Duran et al.&#8217;s paper and I came up with an idea to fix it.</p>
